name: Nutrition App UI
description:
Nutrition is Queen. Exercise is King. Put them together and you've got the kingdom. This is what I did while making this UI Kit. This kit is a product of Love, Passion, Will and Hunger. The kit contains 25+ screens for you.


The screens are designed for an uplabs challenge. If I win this challenge, I will launch it's updated version for free which contains more than 50 screens with components and responsive resizing. So what are you waiting for. Hit the Like Button and help me win this challenge.
